{"tid":676850,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"陳奕迅2018廣東歌","createTime":"2018-05-24T16:57:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-25T06:37:42.000Z","uid":46995,"like":18,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"20cb7ffce9580bd7e27c4933860b6d46bf2ba943","tid":676850,"uid":46995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T16:57:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/EasonChanOfficial/posts/1993168380693365\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FEasonChanOfficial%2Fposts%2F1993168380693365&d=uXFdhwHKVZg4YdekkMzJYW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=a0c3f0f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/EasonChanOfficial/posts/1993168380693365</a><br />\n<br />\nYouTube:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/q6zTYlWxak8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fq6zTYlWxak8&d=uXFdhwHKVZg4YdekkMzJYW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=0a295116\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/q6zTYlWxak8</a><br />\n<br />\nL.O.V.E.的誕生一切緣於2010年DUO世界巡迴演唱會開始&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n2010年DUO世界巡迴演唱會，我們經歷了一趟精彩的音樂旅程，在不同地方留下無數回憶。巡演完結了，我們並沒有各散東西，還約定一起創作屬於eason and the duo band的大碟，L.O.V.E.不單是大碟的名稱，還正正代表我們之間的精神。<br />\n<br />\n今次的專輯是由 eason and the duo band十七位成員親自打造的十一首歌曲集合而成，各首歌曲充滿了我們的個人魅力及對duo band的投入。<br />\n<br />\n而《與你常在》將為這張專輯打開序幕，接下來希望大家與我們一起經歷L.O.V.E.的音樂之旅，慢慢欣賞以下陸續推出屬於eason and the duo band的歌曲。"},{"pid":"d88ebd98b83794ba86b87eda9b32f01308abeda8","tid":676850,"uid":145975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T16:58:59.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"1227b8bb7f27f9da2306437b19d86178c58b4c3b","tid":676850,"uid":77569,"like":1,"dislike":18,"score":-17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T17:07:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"246bd9005d2019276cb8c73e92d22911e733c342","tid":676850,"uid":10903,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T17:09:22.000Z","msg":"正呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72f58b4a1bddd0192366668bf6fca89eebac5236","tid":676850,"uid":118216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T17:23:08.000Z","msg":"在一起會有多美<br />\n在一起也會不美<br />\n一個人 同偕到老不靠運氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n終於出廣東話歌喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c3365ef0f469a40137528ac224c7eb8dc35ae39","tid":676850,"uid":46995,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1227b8bb7f27f9da2306437b19d86178c58b4c3b","tid":676850,"uid":77569,"like":1,"dislike":18,"score":-17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T17:07:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T17:25:35.000Z","msg":"我認係老柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1de3a3701b6988bca6d23b83e5081189f5a48c36","tid":676850,"uid":7865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T17:26:12.000Z","msg":"王雙駿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6361490b71cc83fde12221400e83ebd23421ace3","tid":676850,"uid":8336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T17:32:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 終於出廣東歌"},{"pid":"6449b8a6ba8e059d64307c075bda2c390f74dd1d","tid":676850,"uid":40286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T17:32:14.000Z","msg":"聽緊天下無雙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/